{"version":3,"kind":"Article","sha256":"c4bbe969bd484ec6039bc2994f5f1d16f0ece5f42b3cb14a23594ac37c7abd2b","slug":"qtresearch","location":"/archive/roadmap/drafts/businesses/qtresearch.md","dependencies":[],"frontmatter":{"title":"科研服务业务","content_includes_title":false,"github":"https://github.com/quanttide/quanttide-tech","keywords":["quanttide","documentation"],"numbering":{"title":{"offset":4}},"source_url":"https://github.com/quanttide/quanttide-tech/blob/main/docs/archive/roadmap/drafts/businesses/qtresearch.md","edit_url":"https://github.com/quanttide/quanttide-tech/edit/main/docs/archive/roadmap/drafts/businesses/qtresearch.md","exports":[{"format":"md","filename":"qtresearch.md","url":"/qtresearch-38fce2d0d8a40187af9579e1bb6f713e.md"}]},"mdast":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"block","children":[{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":3,"column":1},"end":{"line":4,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"科研服务业务的服务对象主要是经管科研团队，主要业务范围是提供跨学科科研方向指导、解决技术和数据问题等。\n科研服务业务大量使用我们的云、开源和课程业务的积累，以提高交付质量和效率。","position":{"start":{"line":3,"column":1},"end":{"line":3,"column":1}},"key":"F1BYncrDTB"}],"key":"I5GeZEfgUA"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":6,"column":1},"end":{"line":6,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"一直以来，我主要是在摇摆，重点应该是放在科研的商业服务，还是应该放在经济学本专业的市场应用。这决定了我应该怎么投入资源。","position":{"start":{"line":6,"column":1},"end":{"line":6,"column":1}},"key":"KXGs2APC95"}],"key":"kmcS9lWavu"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":8,"column":1},"end":{"line":8,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"两个方向的共同点是，我都需要控制经管科研的供给。不同点在于，一个是关注产出，一个是关注过程。这两个从战略上是不冲突。从风险角度上，关注过程相对来说更保险。但是从收入角度，科研市场的规模是没有企业服务大的。","position":{"start":{"line":8,"column":1},"end":{"line":8,"column":1}},"key":"MCg3bblOgA"}],"key":"LEcP6BKs6i"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":10,"column":1},"end":{"line":10,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"我自己手上的学术圈资源也是最多的，相比之下也比较容易商业化。在积累充分以后再去做经济咨询业务比较合适。","position":{"start":{"line":10,"column":1},"end":{"line":10,"column":1}},"key":"h95oxFA996"}],"key":"xIVgUTolwa"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":12,"column":1},"end":{"line":12,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"如果维持这个战略方向，则维持科研服务平台和助研平台的建设依然是十分有必要的。","position":{"start":{"line":12,"column":1},"end":{"line":12,"column":1}},"key":"EYWKobV46D"}],"key":"PmYrpP366y"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":14,"column":1},"end":{"line":14,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"科研工作者的交付产出除了论文，往往还有各种软件等等，因此还是需要各种底层接入。","position":{"start":{"line":14,"column":1},"end":{"line":14,"column":1}},"key":"GRnOesIIGO"}],"key":"FuhTB5xWyV"}],"key":"mZUKtYRZzk"}],"key":"DWHV9Leeku"},"references":{"cite":{"order":[],"data":{}}}}